name: ELECTRIC RENAISSANCE
description:
BEEPLE ON MY ASS = LAMBO?

As a degenerate born, child of the internet, I saw the breadcrumbs leading up to the WSB shenanigans and rise of bitcoin in Feb 2021.. It was these two events (and global pandemic) that drove up the price of ethereum and gave rise to the exploding nft art market we see today. 

Every piece I mint feels like a direct F U to Wall St, the artworld needed a shakeup too but they weren't ready for a hoard of meme loving degenerates like us. 😊

Self portrait photography, vectored and digitally edited 👍
